          "canonical": "[ edit | edit source ]\n • Spring Popper can be harvested in the Deepmines Forward Base of Corporate Restructuring Deepmines Bounty .\n • May be awarded randomly as a bonus bounty reward at the end of the mission, appearing just beside the extraction elevator.\n\n• Can be purchased for 10 Fergolyte from Nightcap , requiring Rank 2 - Curious .\n\n | Location\n |\n | Mushroom |\n | Effect\n |\n\n | Deepmines Forward Base\n(Stage 2-5 zone in Corporate Restructuring bounty)\n |\n | Winter Spear\n |\n | Weapons inflict Cold Damage. Greatly increases Movement Speed and Parkour Velocity , and greatly reduces Friction .\n |\n\n | Ironwood\n |\n | Weapons inflict Impact Damage. Player is surrounded by particle effects similar to those of Prism . Enemies hit will likewise produce said particle effects.\n |\n\n | Spring Popper\n |\n | Weapons inflict Blast Damage. Enemies hit by weapons are thrown upwards with a Ragdoll effect.\n |\n\n | Borica\n |\n | Weapons inflict Corrosive Damage.\n |",
